devdoc.details: A simple KYC (Know Your Customer) registry system on blockchain Allows authorized verifiers to update customer KYC status and details

params._officer: Address of the verifier to be added

constructor.details: Constructor sets the contract deployer as owner

createKYC(address,uint256).details: Updates KYC status and details for a customer

getCustomerKYC(address).details: Retrieves KYC information for a customer

returns._0: Customer's KYC status, level, last update timestamp, and verifier address

params._officer: Address of the verifier to be removed

updateKYC(address,bool,bool).details: Updates KYC status and details for a customer
